| Variable           | Example Value                                                         | Description                                          |
| ------------------ | --------------------------------------------------------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------- |
| `AWS_REGION`       | `us-east-1`                                                           | AWS region for all services                          |
| `SQS_QUEUE_URL`    | `https://sqs.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/123456789012/notification-queue` | The queue the worker polls                           |
| `APP_TABLE_NAME`   | `AppTable`                                                            | DynamoDB table name that stores application metadata |
| `SES_FROM_ADDRESS` | `no-reply@yourdomain.com`                                             | Verified email identity in SES                       |
| `POLL_INTERVAL`    | `5`                                                                   | Optional: seconds between SQS polling attempts       |
